reviewText: Finally, a realistic portrayal of the Djinn in a movie. I would go into details but don't want to spoil a well made movie.

A superb French film that alludes to the existence of the djinn.  The actual djinn are never really "fully" shown; but they are presented in their true shadow-world between ours.  The overall plot and ending are what make this film truly worth watching - heartfelt and thought provoking indeed.  Recommended!
